		{
			dependencies: ["59E5F8A65B826B42"]
			description: [
				"The dummy is a great way to test new weapons and abilities in a safe controlled manner. Once placed down, it will not be destroyed by your attacks, and will even display your damage dealt along with DPS."
				"If you do find yourself wanting to move, simply crouch and hit the dummy to break it."
			]
