		}
		{
			dependencies: ["59E5F8A65B826B42"]
			description: [
				"Have you noticed the blue arrow next to your hotbar? One of the most important things to know about combat in this pack is the ability to &6&oroll&r&r."
				"Once assigned to any key in the controls menu (Default: R), pressing it will launch you in the direction you're moving, or forwards if you aren't. The meter will slowly recharge before allowing you to roll again. This is a very helpful skill, and can be key to avoiding some attacks."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			icon: {
				Count: 1
