		{
			dependencies: ["48FD69C56789F0D9"]
			description: [
				"Rolling is great for avoiding many attacks, but there are times you simply need to take the blow. In these cases, a shield is your best ally. Simply holding one in your hands will decrease the damage you take from incoming attacks."
				"But simply holding a shield is one thing. It's another to &6&oblock&r&r with it. Blocking with a shield will completely negate most attacks. Be careful, however, as weapons such as axes may damage your shield, disabling it for a small period of time."
			]
			id: "63FE95E91D565AE0"
