			dependencies: ["59E5F8A65B826B42"]
			description: [
				"Want to avoid the chance of taking damage all together? Or maybe you're wanting to build another stealth archer. Either way, bows are a great method to deal damage from afar."
				"In this pack, they've been upgraded to have &6&ocritical hits&r&r. Whenever you shoot an arrow that's been fully charged, there's a chance you'll deal &6&o50% more damage.&r&r Sneaking while firing an arrow also increases the chance of a critical hit."
				"Guess stealth archers really are strong."
			]
